cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE, cs.IT

The paper deals with the application of deep learning algorithms for medical image analysis, specifically in the context of breast lesion classification using ultrasound images. This falls under the broad category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of transfer learning and data augmentation techniques also suggests a focus on model optimization and training (cs.MM, cs.NE). Finally, the investigation of the impact of image reconstruction algorithms on classification performance indicates a potential interest in information theory (cs.IT).
